metadata.name: Naiu: The Ascended of Envy
metadata.description: Naiu: the Ascended of envy: Naiu was gifted beauty beyond that of most of the Enlighted; her constant pursuit of superior beauty brought an overwhelming feeling of envy of the 2 enlightened entities more beautify than her (one of which was Shaullu). Her punishment was countless lifetimes of humiliation, ridicule and  psychological torment. her perpetual atonement will determine her standing as one of the Ascended
